quran[29]{c,v,t}:
  7,88,"Abanyacyubahiro b’abibone mu bantu be, baravuga bati \"Yewe Shuwayibu! Rwose tuzakwirukana mu mudugudu wacu wowe n’abemeye hamwe na we, cyangwa muze mu idini ryacu\". Aravuga ati \"Ese n’ubwo twaba tutabishaka (mwabiduhatira)"
  7,89,"Mu by’ukuri, turamutse tuje mu idini ryanyu twaba duhimbiye Allah ikinyoma nyuma y’uko Allah yariturinze. Nta n’ubwo dukwiye kurizamo, keretse Allah, Nyagasani wacu abishatse. Nyagasani wacu azi buri kintu cyose. Allah wenyine ni we twiringira. Nyagasani wacu! Dukiranure n’abantu bacu mu kuri, kuko ari wowe mucamanza mwiza"
  7,90,"Abanyacyubahiro bahakanye bo mu bantu be (babuza abantu gukurikira Shuwayibu) bavuga bati \"Nimuramuka mukurikiye Shuwayibu, rwose muzaba muhombye"
  7,91,"Nuko ubwo baba batewe n’umutingito, maze bahinduka imirambo bapfukamye mu mazu yabo"
  7,92,Babandi bahinyuye Shuwayibu babaye nk’aho batigeze baba aho bari batuye (kuko barimbuwe bose). Babandi bahinyuye Shuwayibu ni bo babaye abanyagihombo
  7,93,"Nuko (Shuwayibu) arahindukira abatera umugongo aravuga ati \"Yemwe bantu banjye! Rwose nabagejejeho ubutumwa bwa Nyagasani wanjye mbagira n’inama. Nonese ni gute naterwa agahinda (no kurimbuka) kw’abantu b’abahakanyi"
  7,94,"Kandi ntabwo twohereza umuhanuzi mu mudugudu uwo ariwo wose (ngo ahinyurwe), maze ngo tubure guhanisha abawutuye ubukene n’indwara z’ibyorezo kugira ngo bicishe bugufi (banicuze kuri Allah)"
  7,95,"Nuko imibereho mibi yabo tuyihindura myiza, kugeza ubwo biyongereye baranakungahara, maze baravuga bati \"(Ibi ni na ko byagendaga kuva kera kuko) abakurambere bacu bagerwagaho n’ibibi ndetse n’ibyiza (bidatewe no guhakana)\". Nuko tubagwa gitumo (tubahana) batabizi"
  7,96,"Kandi n’iyo abatuye imidugudu baza kwemera bakanatinya (Allah), mu by’ukuri, twari kubafungurira imigisha iturutse mu kirere no mu isi, ariko barahakanye; nuko tubahanira ibyo bakoraga"
  7,97,"Ese abatuye imidugudu bibwira ko batekanye, ko nta gihano cyacu cyabageraho nijoro baryamye"
  7,98,"Cyangwa abatuye imidugudu bibwira ko batekanye, ko nta gihano cyacu cyabageraho ku gasusuruko bahugiye mu by’isi"
  7,99,"Ese bibwira ko batekanye, badashobora kugerwaho n’ibihano bya Allah? Ntabibwira ko badashobora kugerwaho n’ibihano bya Allah uretse abanyagihombo"
  7,100,"Ese babandi bazunguye ubutaka nyuma y’uko bene bwo (barimbuwe), ntibabona ko iyo tuza kubishaka twari kubahanira ibyaha byabo (nk’uko twabigenje ku bababanjirije), tukanadanangira imitima yabo maze ntibabashe kumva"
  7,101,"Iyo yari imidugudu tukubarira inkuru zayo (yewe Muhamadi). Mu by’ukuri, intumwa zabo zabazaniye ibimenyetso bigaragara ariko ntibashobora kwemera ibyo bahakanye mbere. Uko ni ko Allah adanangira imitima y’abahakanyi"
  7,102,Kandi abenshi muri bo twasanze ari abantu batubahiriza amasezerano; ahubwo twasanze abenshi muri bo ari inkozi z’ibibi
  7,103,"Nuko nyuma (y’izo ntumwa) twohereza Musa kwa Farawo n’abantu be, tunamuha ibitangaza byacu (azifashisha), maze barabihakana. Ngaho irebere uko iherezo ry’abangizi ryagenze"
  7,104,"Nuko Musa aravuga ati \"Yewe Farawo! Mu by’ukuri, njye ndi intumwa yoherejwe na Nyagasani w’ibiremwa byose"
  7,105,Birakwiye ko ntacyo navuga kuri Allah kitari ukuri. Rwose mbazaniye ibitangaza bigaragara biturutse kwa Nyagasani wanyu. Bityo rekura bene Isiraheli bankurikire
  7,106,"(Farawo) aramubwira ati \"Niba hari igitangaza uzanye, ngaho kigaragaze niba koko uri umwe mu banyakuri"
  7,107,"Nuko (Musa) anaga inkoni ye hasi, ihita ihinduka inzoka (nini) igaragara"
  7,108,Anasohora ukuboko kwe (mu kwaha) guhita kwererana ku bari aho babibona
  7,109,"Abanyacyubahiro mu bantu ba Farawo baravuga bati \"Mu by’ukuri, uyu ni umurozi w’umuhanga"
  7,110,"Arashaka kubakura mu gihugu cyanyu\". (Farawo arababaza ati) \"Ese mwangira iyihe nama"
  7,111,"Baramubwira bati \"Ba umwihoreye (ntumwice) we n’umuvandimwe we [Haruna (Aroni)], maze wohereze (ingabo) mu mijyi yose zikoranye (abarozi)"
  7,112,Bazakuzanire buri murozi wese w’umuhanga
  7,113,"Nuko abarozi baza kwa Farawo, baramubwira bati \"Ese turahabwa igihembo nituramuka dutsinze"
  7,114,"(Farawo) aravuga ati \"Ni byo (muzagororerwa), kandi muzaba bamwe mu byegera (byanjye)"
  7,115,"Baravuga bati \"Yewe Musa! (urahitamo) kubanza kunaga (inkoni yawe), cyangwa abe ari twe tubanza kunaga"
  7,116,"(Musa) aravuga ati \"Mwe nimunage\". Nuko banaze, barindagiza amaso y’abantu, banabakura imitima, bagaragaza uburozi buhambaye"